sexual behavior, certain kinds of STIs, travel

00:02:45.599 --> 00:02:49.250
outside of the US within the last few months
to a country where infectious diarrhea is

00:02:49.250 --> 00:02:54.800
a risk, a BMI over 30, antibiotic use in the
past three months, asthma or eczema, history

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:58.300
of irritable bowel syndrome or chronic fatigue
disease, etc

